data.description: Welcome to this newly renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac. It offers 1,207 square feet of living space on a generous 11,608 square foot lot, and it's ready for you to move in.    The property showcases recent upgrades that ensure modern comfort and efficiency. It features new electrical wiring and sockets throughout, enhancing security and energy efficiency with new windows and doors. The re-plumbing work was completed last year, and a brand-new AC and furnace were installed in 2022.    Inside, you'll discover fresh tile and wood laminate flooring, along with fully remodeled bathrooms and kitchen. In 2017 a brand new roof was installed that adds an extra layer of protection to your home.    All the windows and doors are new double pane, enhancing energy efficiency and security. The driveway features attractive pavers, adding to the home's curb appeal. Plus, the spacious backyard is perfect for outdoor enjoyment.    This home comes with great neighbors and privacy, offering a perfect balance. Moreover, it offers easy access to Seminole County walking and bike trails, making it an ideal place where comfort and convenience meet
